xpath

1. for links by using contains

//a[contains(text(), 'value')]--- recommended

2. xpath by using AND operator

//tagname[@attribute name = 'attribute value' and @attribute name = 'attribute value']

3. dynamic xpath for webtable 

//tagname[text()='value']//parent::tagname[@attribute name = 'attribute value']//preceding-sibling::tagname[@attribute name = 'attribute value']//child::tagname[@attribute name = 'attribute value']
